The "cfg80211 [https://wireless.wiki.kernel.org/en/developers/documentation/wireless-extensions wireless extensions] compatibility" option aka WEXT will support old [[Handbook:Parts/Networking/Wireless#Wireless_tools|wireless-tools]] & [https://wireless.wiki.kernel.org/en/users/documentation/iw/replace-iwconfig iwconfig].

